      "description": "This vehicle is in fair overall condition. While it remains a reliable daily driver, it shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some thinning of the clear coat on the hood. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, though the suspension is becoming a bit soft and there is a slow leak from the power steering pump that will eventually need attention. The interior has some staining on the upholstery and the driver's seat shows significant wear. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone who doesn't mind a few imperfections or is looking for a vehicle to fix up over time.",
