      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. Honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014I've babied this car since day one and it's in truly pristine shape! If you've been looking for that perfect, 'like-new' feel without the brand-new price tag, this is the one. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, but it\u2019s ready for a new home. Come take it for a spin and see why I\u2019m so excited about it!",
