    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of the legendary S54-powered chassis. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS system that has been meticulously calibrated for optimal cam timing. This specimen is mechanically flawless, featuring a reinforced rear subframe, fresh rod bearings, and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, providing the telepathic turn-in these cars are known for. With zero paint imperfections and a pristine undercarriage free of oxidative scaling, this is a superlative find for the discerning collector seeking peak naturally aspirated performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
